Package net.runelite.client.plugins.banktags

Interface BankTag

  • public interface BankTag
    A bank tag. Plugins may implement this interface to define custom bank tags. You may register a BankTag with TagManager.registerTag(String, BankTag) to make it searchable in the bank UI and tab interface. You may also set the active bank tag via BankTagsService.openBankTag(BankTag), regardless of if the banktag is registered.
    See Also:
    TagManager.registerTag(String, BankTag), TagManager.unregisterTag(String), BankTagsService.openBankTag(BankTag)
